{"id": "27896", "post": "<div class=\"post-27896 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-acquisitions tag-nexusbytes tag-shared-hosting tag-smallweb tag-smallweb-net\" id=\"post-27896\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/nexusbytes-acquires-smallweb/\" rel=\"bookmark\">NexusBytes Acquires SmallWeb</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/acquisitions/\" rel=\"tag\">acquisitions</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/nexusbytes/\" rel=\"tag\">nexusbytes</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/shared-hosting/\" rel=\"tag\">shared hosting</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/smallweb/\" rel=\"tag\">smallweb</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/smallweb-net/\" rel=\"tag\">smallweb.net</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> August 2, 2021 @ 12:00 am, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-26622 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1.png.webp\" alt=\"NexusBytes\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/nexusbytes-1-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">SmallWeb <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/172985/smallweb-has-been-acquired-by-nexusbytes-llc/p1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">announced Friday</a> that they are being acquired by <a href=\"https://nexusbytes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"NexusBytes\">NexusBytes</a>, effective August 1, 2021.</p><p>Full details are available in an email sent to customers, which has also been posted on LowEndTalk.</p><p>Michael, the CEO of SmallWeb, said:</p><p><em>\u201cI\u2019m very proud of what I\u2019ve created and now that we have been an active brand in the community for these years it is sadly time for me to step down and pass the torch on to somebody who won\u2019t just maintain the brand, but improve it and grow it to levels that I unfortunately cannot do by myself.\u201d</em></p><p>We recently covered SmallWeb\u2019s <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/smallweb-suffers-catastrophic-data-loss-in-london/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">London datacenter issue</a>, and during that crisis, Nexus Bytes posted in the thread that they were <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/comment/3257905/#Comment_3257905\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the upstream provider</a> referenced.</p><p>NexusBytes intends to run SmallWeb as a separate brand.&nbsp; We recently <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/interview-qa-with-nexus-bytes-ceo-nahian-on-the-hosting-industry-and-a-customer-first-approach/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndBox\">interviewed NexusBytes\u2019 CEO</a> and featured them in a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CuYrN-yU8x0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube\">LowEndBoxTV Provider Spotlight</a>.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-containe